Exercise  1:  Joy Cursor

Included Files:

	Joy_cursor.cpp
	README

Accessories:

	Arduino Mega2560
	TFT Display
	Joy Stick

Wiring instruction:

	port A8 and A9 should be connected to VRY and VRX respectively,
	and GND to GND, +5V to +5V and port 53 on arduino to SW.

Running instrucion:

	Connect the TFT display on top of arduino such that +5V is connected to
	+5V port and then connect the arduino to your laptop and use the command
	Make upload to see the result